    title: "Ignatius Book Fairs: Benefiting Children and Schools",
    slug: "ignatius-book-fairs-benefiting-children-and-schools",
    summary: "At schools across the country, Ignatius Book Fairs offer children the best titles in literature, from wholesome works to wholesome classics! In addition to students, Ignatius Book Fairs supports schools through the “Ave Dollars” rewards program",
    content: "<p id=\">At schools across the country, Ignatius Book Fairs offer children the best titles in literature, from wholesome works to wholesome classics! In addition to students, Ignatius Book Fairs supports schools through the “<em id=\">Ave Dollars</em>” rewards program. Now, every purchase at your school’s Ignatius Book Fair goes to directly benefit your school! </p><p id=\">‍</p><h4 id=\"><strong id=\">Benefiting Your Children</strong> | Getting Wholesome Titles in the Hands of Your Children </h4><p id=\"><strong id=\">How are our titles selected? </strong></p><p id=\">Every title offered by Ignatius Book Fairs has been carefully vetted to ensure that safe, wholesome content reaches the hands of your children. These books are filled with enriching stories that feature upstanding characters and role models. After these books have been successfully screened, they land on the shelves of our Fair, ready to inspire and deepen your child’s faith!</p><p id=\">‍</p><p id=\">‍</p><p id=\"> </p><p id=\"> </p><h4 id=\"><strong id=\">Benefiting Your School </strong>| Rewards for Each Book Purchased </h4><p id=\"><strong id=\">How do “<em id=\">Ave Dollars</em>” work? </strong></p><p id=\">With every purchase you make at an Ignatius Book Fair, your school earns <em id=\">Ave Dollars</em>, a currency that can be used to purchase books or other classroom resources through Ignatius Book Fairs! These books can be used to grow your school, classroom, or parish library. <em id=\">Ave Dollars</em> makes it possible for both your school and children to benefit from the Fair even after it has ended! </p><p id=\">‍</p><div data-rt-embed-type='true'><p style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #0088ff;\">Ignatius Book Fair Tip: Ave Dollars can also be redeemed for cash back for your school! </p></div><p id=\">‍</p><p id=\">Interested in our books? Make a visit to <a href=\"https://www.ignatiusbookfairs.com/post/upcoming-ignatius-book-fairs-near-you\" id=\">a Book Fair near you,</a> or <a href=\"https://shop.ignatiusbookfairs.com/\" id=\"><em id=\">shop.ignatiusbookfairs.com</em></a> to review our collection of wholesome and inspiring titles! </p><p id=\">To host a book fair at your school, please fill out an inquiry form at <a href=\"https://www.ignatiusbookfairs.com/\" id=\"><em id=\">ignatiusbookfairs.com! </em> </a></p><p id=\"> </p><p id=\">‍</p>",
