    content: "<p id=\">Ignatius Book Fairs was established to aid families in their search for truthful and virtuous children’s literature! Every Ignatius Book Fair offers a plethora of faithful and wholesome stories centered around beauty, virtue, and goodness. Here are three reasons why Ignatius Book Fairs are a safe choice for parents: </p><ol start=\"1\" id=\"><li id=\"><strong id=\">Each Fair Features Curated and Wholesome Content </strong> </li></ol><p id=\">Ignatius Book Fairs is dedicated to providing wholesome content for Christian families. Because of this, each title offered at an Ignatius Book Fair is specifically curated to accomplish this mission! Every book has been intentionally chosen to encourage virtue and faithfulness, while also giving children quality entertainment. Ignatius Book Fairs, by combining exceptional content with authentic Catholic faith, provides parents with literature they can trust!</p><ol start=\"2\" id=\"><li id=\"><strong id=\">Each Story Supports Catholic Values</strong> </li></ol><p id=\">At many mainstream book fairs, children’s content is guided and shaped by modern culture. However, at Ignatius Book Fairs, all literature is grounded in the rich truth of the Catholic faith and the tradition of Christ’s Church. Although the world rejects traditional beliefs and family values, Ignatius Book Fairs continues to offer books that proclaim the truth rooted in Christ. </p><blockquote id=\"><em id=\">“That’s our promise to parents, that anything that you find at an Ignatius Book Fair will be something that you can trust” —Rose Trabbic, IBF&nbsp;Director of Operations</em></blockquote><ol start=\"3\" id=\"><li id=\"><strong id=\">Tools to Enhance Catholic Family Life </strong> </li></ol><p id=\">Ignatius Book Fairs features numerous books for families hoping to integrate the faith into their everyday life! As <em id=\">The Catechism of the Catholic Church</em> states, the family is a “domestic church” and it needs wholesome entertainment that enriches the goodness of the home. While adhering to the Church’s teachings, Ignatius Book Fairs intentionally aims to build up Catholic family life. </p><p id=\">Parents striving to raise virtuous children deserve content they can trust! Ignatius Book Fairs is committed to offering books that won’t contradict the Christian faith, nor the importance of the family. Ultimately, Ignatius Book Fairs provides a sanctuary for Catholics seeking a nourishing, enriching, and wholesome environment to support their children through the power of literature.</p>",
